data.description: Well maintained home conveniently located in the desirable neighborhood of Avalon Park with quick access to I-10, Pensacola, and Gulf Breeze. This home has a private split floor plan with a large master bedroom, double bowl vanity, soaker tub/shower and two walk-in closets. The kitchen has a hop up bar that is open to the living room and an informal eat-in kitchen area. A flex room makes a great dining area, den, or office. The large backyard will accommodate your boat or RV, and there is a 30 AMP receptacle for power. A 12 X 24 shed was added within the fenced-in backyard for additional storage or a workshop space. The new owners will enjoy all the benefits of energy efficient solar panels, and a reduced electric bill. There is no HOA in this quiet, cul-de-sac community - go see it today!
